<div class='commit-subject'>renderer: fix heap overflow in vertex elements state create</div><div class='commit-msg'>The 'num_elements' can be controlled by the guest but the
'vrend_vertex_element_array' has a fixed 'elements' field.
This can cause a heap overflow. Add sanity check of 'num_elements'.

